a pixel electrode electrically connected to the other one of the source and drain regions,
wherein the gate line comprises aluminum and contains oxygen atoms at a concentration of 8×1018 atoms/cm3 or less, carbon atoms at a concentration of 5×1018 atoms/cm3 or less, and nitrogen atoms at a concentration of 7×1017 atoms/cm3 or less.

